Package: palaeorotate
Type: Package
Title: An R package providing reconstruction files for plate rotation models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
     person("Lewis A.", "Jones", 
     email = "LewisAlan.Jones@uvigo.es",
     role = c("aut", "cre"), 
     comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3902-8986"))
Description: The palaeorotate R package provides reconstruction files for a
      1&deg; x 1&deg; spatial grid for various plate rotation models.
      An uncertainty file, providing the range in reconstructed 
      palaeocoordinates between all reconstruction files is also provided.
License: GPL (>= 3)
